      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped hake</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cornflour </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up so the hake is fully coated</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining cornflour</strong> to a separate bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> coated hake</strong> to the bowl with the remaining cornflour and give everything a good mix up until all the hake is coated</p>",
