            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> and set aside, then shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of <strong>carrot ribbons</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1692024624289-x200.jpg",
